# kart.info for an unknown kart on a freshly initialized (or unused)
# garage returns kart_not_found (code 3). This proves:
#   - kart.info is registered (no method_not_found)
#   - param binding works (name required)
#   - the handler merges garage + devpod and correctly diagnoses "absent
#     from both sides" as not_found rather than stale.
#
# The test assumes devpod, if present on PATH, reports an empty workspace
# list for a fresh $HOME — true in CI and in the devcontainer sandbox.

stdin info.json
lakitu rpc
! stderr .
stdout '"error":'
! stdout 'method_not_found'
stdout '"code":3'
stdout '"type":"kart_not_found"'
stdout '"kart":"ghost"'

-- info.json --
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"kart.info","params":{"name":"ghost"},"id":1}
